font : font-style font-variant font-weight font-size/line-height font-family

A forward slash, /, separator is needed between the font-size and line-height property values.

text-indent

text-shadow:  horizontal offset, vertical offset, a blur and a color

text-transform - none, capitalize, uppercase, lowercase, and inherit

letter-spacing
word-spacing

Web-Safe Fonts http://learn.shayhowe.com/html-css/working-with-typography/#web-safe-fonts

Embedding Web Fonts
@font-face {
  font-family: "Lobster";
  src: local("Lobster"), url("lobster.woff") format("woff");
}
body {
  font-family: "Lobster", "Comic Sans", cursive;
}
https://fonts.google.com/


Including Citations & Quotes http://learn.shayhowe.com/html-css/working-with-typography/#citations-quotes
    <cite>: Used to reference a creative work, author, or resource
    <q>: Used for short, inline quotations
    <blockquote>: Used for longer external quotations
